#xA;  WordFill&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#wordfill&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&amp;amp;fname=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.kakaocdn.net%2Fdna%2FRz9B1%2FbtsPM13sHmV%2FAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAFNDjl4c8njpb6wh8LkMaDagD9JHi81ZXsfAasdnB9ON%2Fimg.jpg%3Fcredential%3DyqXZFxpELC7KVnFOS48ylbz2pIh7yKj8%26expires%3D1756652399%26allow_ip%3D%26allow_referer%3D%26signature%3Dxc%252Fd2JEhHE%252B%252FG7MDl3FYTIoPtOc%253D&#34; alt=&#34;WordFill&#34; title=&#34;WordFill&#34;/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;If there is a value in the right side of the selected reference column, fill the cell value in a DB format.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;alldecimals&#34;&gt;&#xA;  allDecimals&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#alldecimals&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&amp;amp;fname=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.kakaocdn.net%2Fdna%2FbX7uV2%2FbtsPO7avOIW%2FAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAHdSU_uW8CujPEk4UW2mBR0_lTLCmuvkCQ3u1XWO58LZ%2Fimg.jpg%3Fcredential%3DyqXZFxpELC7KVnFOS48ylbz2pIh7yKj8%26expires%3D1756652399%26allow_ip%3D%26allow_referer%3D%26signature%3DB99sDNUwLjY2pjh0sc0fjzf3zNY%253D&#34; alt=&#34;allDecimals&#34; title=&#34;allDecimals&#34;/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;In the case of numbers with decimal points, all decimal points come out.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;shownamelist&#34;&gt;&#xA;  shownamelist&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#shownamelist&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&amp;amp;fname=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.kakaocdn.net%2Fdna%2Ftsdsf%2FbtsPQAbXZJl%2FAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAEsquOYqTusetlkB0kriGB-MoRhBwGOjrxkt6WMKJdEN%2Fimg.jpg%3Fcredential%3DyqXZFxpELC7KVnFOS48ylbz2pIh7yKj8%26expires%3D1756652399%26allow_ip%3D%26allow_referer%3D%26signature%3DZ%252BJGZnON%252F1Oi%252BoU8pp0Qm2qulns%253D&#34; alt=&#34;shownamelist&#34; title=&#34;show